OL,7,FThe real people behind the characters
OL,8,Fbecame household names and regular
OL,9,Ffixtures on our screens.
OL,11,FBut some, like forensic accountant Kay
OL,12,FLinnell and her business partner
OL,13,FBarbara Jeremiah, preferred to fly
OL,14,Funder the radar.
