OL,7,FFeatured in the drama "rolled together
OL,8,Fas one character", Barbara said, the
OL,9,Fduo are long-term supporters of and
OL,10,Fadvisors to the Justice for
OL,11,FSubpostmasters Alliance, and despite
OL,12,Ftheir aversion to personal publicity,
OL,13,Fthe two women were instrumental in
OL,14,Fhelping to bring the Horizon scandal
OL,15,Fto light.
OL,17,FIn their first on-camera interview,
OL,18,Fthey tell us how it all began.
OL,20,F"It all started with Barbara," Kay
OL,21,Fsaid.
