OL,7,F"Because Jo Hamilton is our local sub-
OL,8,Fpostmistress and Barbara used to buy
OL,9,Flunch on the way to work from Jo."
OL,11,FBarbara was there when Jo began
OL,12,Fsuffering shortfalls on Horizon.
OL,14,F"I found Jo increasingly agitated when
OL,15,Fher Horizon system was doubling and
OL,16,Fdoubling and doubling," said Barbara.
