OL,7,FWhen Jo was convicted in 2007, Barbara
OL,8,Fand other members of the small
OL,9,FHampshire village where Jo's Post
OL,10,FOffice was, never believed Jo could
OL,11,Fhave been guilty, and immediately
OL,12,Fsupported her.
OL,14,F"It took me a couple of years to
OL,15,Fconvince (Kay) that we needed a
OL,16,Fforensic accountant," Barbara said.
