OL,7,FBut eventually, Kay agreed, and they
OL,8,Fboth became advisors to the Justice
OL,9,Ffor Sub-postmasters Alliance (JFSA),
OL,10,Fthe campaign group set up by Sir Alan
OL,11,FBates.
OL,13,FThey have also worked alongside Second
OL,14,FSight Investigators Ron Warmington and
OL,15,FIan Henderson since 2012, when Second
OL,16,FSight were appointed by the Post
OL,17,FOffice to look into potential issues
OL,18,Fwith the Horizon system.
OL,20,FThroughout, their support for the sub-
OL,21,Fpostmasters has never wavered.
