OL,7,F"It's their story," Kay told us.
OL,8,F"We're the support behind them. The
OL,9,Fmessage is their story, it's not ours.
OL,10,FWe're not trying to grab the
OL,11,Flimelight."
OL,13,FKay and Barbara both know where their
OL,14,Fskills lie.
OL,16,F"We're quite good at finding the
OL,17,Fnumbers," Kay said.
