OL,12,FSo, what made them want to finally
OL,13,Fspeak publicly about the scandal? As
OL,14,Falways, it comes back to the sub-
OL,15,Fpostmasters.
OL,17,F"I hope it helps them get their
OL,18,Fmoney." Kay said.
OL,20,FMoney which, in their view, is coming
OL,21,Ffar too late.
