OL,7,F"Of the 555 (sub-postmasters who were
OL,8,Fpart of the Mr Bates vs the Post
OL,9,FOffice group litigation), 64 have died
OL,10,Fwithout any redress at all," Barbara
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"You can't imagine the stories they've
OL,14,Fbeen through...they are fighting for
OL,15,Fjustice," Barbara said.
OL,17,FWhat sub-postmasters have been through
OL,18,Fis "amazingly awful" and there is an
OL,19,F"underlying anger at the
OL,20,Fmaltreatment," Kay added.
