OL,7,FThe fight for full and fair
OL,8,Fcompensation continues. As of
OL,9,FSeptember 2024, compensation offers
OL,10,Fhad been made to less than half of the
OL,11,FGLO group of 555 sub-postmasters.
OL,13,FKay and Barbara's support for the sub-
OL,14,Fpostmasters is unwavering.
OL,16,F"They know they can ring up our office
OL,17,Fand we will never turn any of them
OL,18,Faway," Kay told us.
