OL,7,FGiven the extraordinary amount of time
OL,8,Fthat the duo have spent working with
OL,9,Fthe JFSA, how has their involvement
OL,10,Faffected their professional life?
OL,12,F"It's a hobby that has got out of
OL,13,Fhand," Kay laughs.
OL,15,FAside from financial redress, Kay and
OL,16,FBarbara are determined to hold those
OL,17,Fresponsible for Britain's biggest
OL,18,Fmiscarriage of justice accountable.
