OL,7,F"The thing we'd very much like to do
OL,8,Fis find out whose neglect this
OL,9,Fhappened under and make sure they face
OL,10,Fthe same consequences they put the sub-
OL,11,Fpostmasters through," Kay said.
OL,13,FOf potential criminal charges, she
OL,14,Fadded: "The Metropolitan Police are
OL,15,Fwaiting with some names on their
OL,16,Fbooks."
OL,18,FUltimately, what matters the most to
OL,19,Fthese two women, who have been with
OL,20,Fthe sub-postmasters in their decades-
OL,21,Flong fight to be heard, is justice.
